{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place sugar, unsweetened cocoa powder, cornflour, milk and butter in mixing bowl then cook <b>10 min\/90°C\/speed 4<b>.","Brush 6 ramekins or serving glasses (6 cm diameter) with water or rum to wet the sides. Transfer pudding mixture to ramekins or serving glasses. Allow to cool for 15 minutes then cover with cling film and place into refrigerator to set for a minimum 6 hours or overnight. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Once puddings are set, <strong>insert butterfly whisk.<\/strong> Place cream in mixing bowl and whip <b>until soft peaks form\/speed 3<b>, watching cream carefully through hole in mixing bowl lid to avoid over-whipping. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk.<\/strong> ","Carefully turn out puddings onto 6 individual serving plates, soaking the base of your ramekins in hot water for a few seconds to loosen if required or serve straight from serving glass. Serve puddings immediately with a dollop of whipped cream on top or on the side."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["120 - 150 g caster sugar, adjust to taste","70 g cocoa powder, unsweetened","70 g maize flour","750 g whole milk","60 g unsalted butter, diced","1 Tbsp water","200 g cream, 35-37 % fat, to serve"]}],"id":"r252877","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-dYWk_n0O6ZY\/XZWe1UMF5yI\/AAAAAAAAe6g\/PumP-hQZYy0wqwyxboMPzmfncvD5-6EpgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ib82gcNLm0XwvUBu.png","title":"Chocolate Pudding","publishedAt":"2017-09-25T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7.3 g","fat":"25.9 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"46.1 g","calories":"1859 kJ \/ 442 kcal"},"usefulItems":"ramekins (Ø 6 cm), pastry brush, cling film, serving plate, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["These puddings are a great dessert to make a day ahead as they will keep well in the refrigerator overnight. Simply whip your cream just before serving to have a dessert on the table in minutes when entertaining.","To make this a gluten free recipe, use a certified gluten free cornflour. Always read the labels of your products to ensure no wheat or gluten has been used as part of the production process."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","6h 30m","6 portions"]}